                    <span>I'm a professional graphic/web designer, and I purchased this book to improve my photoshop skills.  Most design books rehash the same old tired stuff, but not this one.  It has many new and interesting projects that will keep right brainers happy and inspired.  I highly recommend it to anyone who is interested in graphical art. I'm so glad that I purchased it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Finally!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
