                    <span>PhotoShop for Right-Brainers is the art of photo manipulation at its finest. Al  Ward clearly and explicitly takes the learner step-by-step through different techniques enabling the reader to advance his/her proficiency in huge leaps with each chapter. Each technique and tool Al explains is accompanied by a picture to elaborate his words. The knowledge and insights from Al's book will give each learners' PhotoShop skills advance life. Huge thanks to Al Ward.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent book!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
